your chain of command.

30:06.931 --> 30:10.931
-Well, Cate's grounded
and this place doesn't suit him.
-(notification chimes)

30:11.013 --> 30:13.847
Fraser needs to spend
time with, you know,

30:13.931 --> 30:16.055
grown-up males.

30:16.138 --> 30:19.389
Someone who can be
like an older brother
or father figure.

30:20.263 --> 30:22.847
Jonathan is a very
nice young man.

30:27.263 --> 30:30.555
I was hoping for a bit of
a truce, at least with you.

30:34.472 --> 30:37.555
