better than your truce.

30:39.347 --> 30:41.972
Sarah:
Sweetheart, I don't...

30:42.055 --> 30:44.764
-You can't know.
-That's right.

30:46.389 --> 30:48.806
Can't know.

30:48.889 --> 30:51.222
Can't ever know.

31:02.222 --> 31:05.430
