♪ I want it ♪

39:05.889 --> 39:07.806
♪ That way ♪

39:07.889 --> 39:09.389
(cheering)

39:24.389 --> 39:27.097
-(cuts engine)
-(car doors shut, open)

39:30.430 --> 39:32.931
Say goodbye to it.

39:33.013 --> 39:36.138
(thudding)

39:43.931 --> 39:45.263
(thud)

39:46.472 --> 39:48.347
-Dad.
-Shower?

39:48.430 --> 39:50.347
-Yeah.
-Aw,

39:50.430 --> 39:52.639
my beautiful baby.
(chuckles)

39:54.972 --> 39:56.472
Come on.

39:59.138 --> 40:00.764
-(laughing)
-Fraser: Let's go back!

40:00.847 --> 40:03.722
Let's put together a band
and fucking make a record!

40:03.806 --> 40:05.972
And let's send a signed
copy to your father!

40:06.055 --> 40:09.847
Jonathan:
Fraser Wilson,
you're a nut case.

40:09.931 --> 40:11.722
Fraser:
(sighs) This was
the most incredible day

40:11.806 --> 40:14.472
-of my whole fucking life!
-(laughs)

40:15.597 --> 40:16.681
(chuckles)

40:18.555 --> 40:19.639
(kiss)

40:19.972 --> 40:21.639
(giggles)

40:23.639 --> 40:24.806
(door shuts)

40:28.806 --> 40:30.097
(keys rattle)

40:30.597 --> 40:32.722
Try to act sober!

40:32.806 --> 40:34.847
(door opening)

40:36.972 --> 40:38.389
-(sighs)
