40:45.180 --> 40:47.430
(humming):
You are...

40:47.514 --> 40:49.639
my fire...

40:50.180 --> 40:51.972
The one...

40:52.681 --> 40:55.180
Desire...

40:55.931 --> 40:57.472
(humming)

40:58.097 --> 41:00.055
When I say...

41:02.847 --> 41:05.514
(humming)

41:08.222 --> 41:12.222
I want it that way...

41:13.430 --> 41:16.222
(humming)

41:17.889 --> 41:20.972
-(curtain rattles)
-(turns on water)

41:21.055 --> 41:22.847
(humming continues)

41:23.847 --> 41:25.514
Fuck!

41:27.639 --> 41:30.055
(humming)

41:30.138 --> 41:32.180
-(door opens)
-Huh?

41:33.514 --> 41:36.472
-What are you doing!? Mom!
-How was it?

41:36.555 --> 41:37.681
Get out!

