43:32.889 --> 43:34.681
Oh no, I'm okay.

43:36.555 --> 43:39.138
-How was hunting?
-Uh, great.

43:39.222 --> 43:41.889
I learned I was
holding my head wrong.

43:41.972 --> 43:43.889
Your father's
an excellent marksman.

43:46.764 --> 43:48.847
You still wanna
be a soldier?

43:48.931 --> 43:50.514
Uh, maybe.

43:52.138 --> 43:54.097
And does your father know
when you say soldier,

43:54.180 --> 43:56.389
you mean male soldier?

