-Do you know Dr. Harris?
-Psychologist?

44:06.347 --> 44:09.555
He's actually
an endocrinologist.

44:09.639 --> 44:13.055
I can take you to see
him, just to talk.

44:14.305 --> 44:16.180
Why?

44:16.263 --> 44:18.806
Sarah:
Because it's time we
changed this world,

44:18.889 --> 44:21.972
and ourselves.

44:22.055 --> 44:25.263
In order to do that,
we have to know ourselves.

44:27.097 --> 44:29.013
I was holding onto
this until I saw you.

44:32.639 --> 44:34.722
Wow.

44:35.972 --> 44:38.722
Take it!
Look it over! Please.

