BE VERY NERVE-WRACKING,

45:25.347 --> 45:28.013
IS, AGAIN, FIND
THE SPOT ON YOUR LEG.

45:28.097 --> 45:30.055
YOU'RE GONNA RELAX YOUR LEG,
TAKE A DEEP BREATH,

45:30.138 --> 45:32.555
POSITION YOUR HAND COMFORTABLY,
YOU'RE GONNA WANNA GRIP IT.

45:32.639 --> 45:34.639
ONE, TWO, THREE.

45:36.681 --> 45:38.222
ALL THE WAY IN.

45:38.305 --> 45:40.430
AND YOU'RE GONNA
WANNA DRAW BACK,
MAKE SURE THERE'S NO BLOOD...

45:40.514 --> 45:42.722
Jennifer:
Could've at least
brought something back!

45:42.806 --> 45:45.722
Richard:
Last time we did, you got all
upset because it was a pheasant.

45:45.806 --> 45:48.889
-(video continues)
-(indistinct arguing)

45:48.972 --> 45:51.138
-(shuts door)
-SLOWLY.

45:51.222 --> 45:54.222
-(muffled arguing)
-AND WE'RE GOOD.

45:54.305 --> 45:56.305
YOU'RE JUST
GONNA TAKE YOUR...

45:56.389 --> 45:59.222
Jennifer:
Why did you have to throw your
clothes in the laundry bag?

45:59.305 --> 46:01.931
AND ONCE THAT'S DONE, YOU'RE
GOING TO MASSAGE THE AREA,

46:02.013 --> 46:04.681
-AND KINDA HELP
SPREAD THE TESTOSTERONE.
-(arguing continues)

46:04.764 --> 46:05.764
(beep)

46:05.847 --> 46:09.597
♪ ♪

